{
  "stem": "15962.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We crossed the Danube on the-- I think the same railway bridge-- because I don't recall that there was any other bridge standing at that time-- and moved away from the Danube on the other bank.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this was our second and fortunately last death march that lasted three days and two nights.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We were mixed in to-- with the Austrian Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were again guards that were ordered to shoot those who couldn't keep up with the group.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was a fairly disorderly kind of procession that went through the countryside and through little villages and little towns.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The first day was extremely hot, and we were extremely thirsty.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there were instances where we tried-- the prisoners tried to get water at farmhouses.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the farmers would chase them away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There were field kitchens.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And in the evening, we did get some soup and some bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We got--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were on-- on wheels.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were military kitchens that preceded us, that cooked some sort of soup.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I recall the second night, we all stayed in a-- outside, in a meadow, in a field.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the last day and a half, the weather changed, and it was just pouring incessantly.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were completely drenched and apathetic and really felt helpless and at the end of our strengths and lacked the will to-- to continue.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But something [BACKROUND NOISE] kept us going, in the hope that we will indeed arrive in a dry place and perhaps be able to lie down and get something to eat.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] We [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] did not know exactly where we were going.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
